            "body": "FYI, git bisect tells that the first bad commit is faa7c15b5a711435ed9d90f7fbf2a2ff8f1255c7 (#39247). This is a regression introduced in v0.12.2; it was working fine for me in v0.12.1. \n\nHowever, the root cause would be the use of `feedkeys <Esc>` (since when the line was first written in #38044); so #39462 seems be a good fix.",
